jeus.servlet.tcp

Class TCPServletResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • jeus.servlet.engine.HttpServletResponseImpl
      • jeus.servlet.tcp.TCPServletResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse, javax.servlet.ServletResponse

    public class TCPServletResponse
extends jeus.servlet.engine.HttpServletResponseImpl
    TCPServlet.service(TCPServletRequest,TCPServletResponse)의 인자로 사용되는 클래스이다. javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse를 implements한 클래스로서 javax.servlet.ServletResponse, javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse 의 모든 method를 호출할 수 있다. 그러나 TCPServlet의 특성상 method의 동작이 다를 수 있다.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form

      • closeOnExit

        public void closeOnExit()
        terminates the physical connection between the TCP client and TCP listener after finishing the request. this method is useful if TCPDispatcherConfig.isPersistentConnection() returns true, but the developer wants to disconnect client connection.
